{"tid":1153810,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"已經好耐無訓過好覺","createTime":"2019-05-14T01:08:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T12:32:44.000Z","uid":199983,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d4e76e704a90e94cd494baedd0c4a57ff62fc589","tid":1153810,"uid":199983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T01:08:25.000Z","msg":"對上一次訓得好係我做完個小手術，嗰陣食啲藥會有睡意，一覺訓天光，唔會發夢<br />\n<br />\n手術嘅再之前都係病嗰陣有醫生開啲有睡意嘅藥先會訓得好<br />\n<br />\n平時係已經好攰，唔玩手機望天花板個幾鐘都訓唔著<br />\n<br />\n訓著咗一個幾鐘就會札醒，即使係依一個幾鐘都會發夢，唔睇下個時間我以爲我訓咗幾分鐘，個人勁攰<br />\n<br />\n有諗過去睇醫生開安眠藥物（？），但係如果靠藥物去訓我又驚會有依賴嘅問題，以後唔食藥就訓唔到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3811bd696904fb95dabdbc1421e41fdf2d88e84f","tid":1153810,"uid":253005,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T01:09:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd200c6250d3e5e67e0612b1d9dac53cec5dfa97","tid":1153810,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T01:21:38.000Z","msg":"有無試過做中強度運動, 慢跑之類. <br />\n唔好係訓前做"},{"pid":"3d111c5f5854759fe0a25fa67db1061983bac82c","tid":1153810,"uid":199983,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cd200c6250d3e5e67e0612b1d9dac53cec5dfa97","tid":1153810,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T01:21:38.000Z","msg":"有無試過做中強度運動, 慢跑之類. <br />\n唔好係訓前做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:42:38.000Z","msg":"有試過，以前有用"},{"pid":"2c11ef81ef249c38c57c63b0908599d492dc8cd2","tid":1153810,"uid":44184,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T11:04:55.000Z","msg":"精神壓力?"},{"pid":"36544b732b8810b53cc6d3f98cf5030d54775b3d","tid":1153810,"uid":191453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2c11ef81ef249c38c57c63b0908599d492dc8cd2","tid":1153810,"uid":44184,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T11:04:55.000Z","msg":"精神壓力?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T11:06:46.000Z","msg":"樓主痴綠佬㴝"},{"pid":"9590ee2d83efb6034fa333454c9